title: Nine Inch Nails - M2 Fragility 2.0 tour special NTSC DVD
description:
9 years ago today (1999.09.09), Nine Inch Nails returned to the stage with the first live performance of the Fragile era.  In honor of this anniversary, I&#039;m proud to present you with the Mtv 2 Fragility 2.0 tour special.  Originally aired 2000.05.27, the special is comprised of approximately 2 hours of videos, live footage, and interviews.

This is an NTSC format DVD.

If you try selling this on ebay, I hope you get cancer.

P.S. - The 9 year anniversary of The Fragile is just around the corner.
